o\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \b LP\b0\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \uc2 Ernst & Young\uc2  Entrepreneur of the Year is celebrating its 25th anniversary, writes \uc2 Maria Pinelli\uc2  .\par \par \uc2 In those years, it has expanded to 140 cities in 50 countries - representing about 93 per cent of the global economy - with awards presented annually to more than 900 of the most successful entrepreneurs.\par \cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\pard \qr \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \b TD\b0\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \uc2 These regional and national award programmes culminate with the announcement of the World Entre--preneur of the Year, which took place on June 4 in Monte Carlo in the 11th year of its existence. Past winners include Michael Spencer of Icap, Narayana Murthy of \uc2 Infosys\uc2  and Guy Lalibert\u233\'00\'E9 of \uc2 Cirque du Soleil\uc2 .\par \par \uc2 So how do the judges go about crowning just one world entrepreneur?\par \par \uc2 Independent judging panels in each region and country evaluate entrepreneurs selected via Entrepreneur of the Year. Each country winner goes through to the global contest and is then re-evaluated by a separate judging panel, which is rotated annually. Over the past decade, the panel has mostly comprised past country winners, which means they understand the challenges entrepreneurs face and the importance of an unbiased judging process.\par \par \uc2 Each judge receives a detailed history of the country winners and meets the finalists in formal interviews and at informal social events to hear their stories. The panel then convenes to rate candidates for six traits:\par \par \uc2 \u8226\'20\'22 Entrepreneurial spirit: examples of perseverance and fresh thinking; how they have overcome obstacles;\par \par \uc2 \u8226\'20\'22 Financial performance: today and their past record; their strategies for long-term sustainability;\par \par \uc2 \u8226\'20\'22 Strategic direction: how they are turning their visions into reality; their goals for growth; how they differentiate themselves;\par \par \uc2 \u8226\'20\'22 Global impact: what the business's impact has been in terms of revenue, operations and influence;\par \par \uc2 \u8226\'20\'22 Innovation: whether entrepreneurs anticipate and embrace change; whether there is continuous improvement and innovation throughout the business;\par \par \uc2 \u8226\'20\'22 Personal integrity and influence: whether there is a culture of \b \highlight22\uc2 corporate social responsibility\b0 \highlight\uc2 ; the business's impact on the \b \highlight22\uc2 environment\b0 \highlight\uc2 ; and whether entrepreneurs' efforts have resulted in improved quality of life in the wider community. \uc2 Maria Pinelli\uc2  is global vice-chairwoman for strategic growth markets at \uc2 Ernst & Young\par \cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\pard \qr \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 \b CO\b0\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 cirsol : \uc2 Le Cirque du Soleil Inc | erwn : \uc2 Ernst & Young LLP\cell \pard \ql \li0\ri0\widctlpar\intbl\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin0 {  \trowd\trgaph15\trqc\trleft-15 \clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx720\clvertalt\clpadl15\clpadr-15 \cellx9360\row} \tro